    "gp_section_625369882908688947": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369882908688947",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "c2750ecda1cc3311996de9276045a9c285c151a82c9787d089c57f2eee885186_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_0": "<p>Item Details</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_1": "<p>Shipping Info</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_2": "<p>Satisfaction Guarantee</p>",
        "ggMOFdfwuZp_text": "<p>Capture your furry friend's unique personality in a vibrant, custom photo tropical style <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/collections/personalized-beach-gift\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hawaii Shirt</strong></a>! Perfect for the cat lover in your life, it also makes a memorable summer or beach trip gift! Make memories that last with this one-of-a-kind fashion statement!<br> </p><p>Every <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/collections/personalized-photo-gifts\"><span style=\"color:rgb(22,95,83);\">personalized photo gift</span></a> is special and unique because we upload your photo, which allows you to express exactly how you want your gift to look</p><p><strong>Preview</strong>:<br>- Choose an option and upload your photo.<br>- Click [<strong>Preview Your Personalization</strong>] to see the preview.<br>- Double-check your options before purchasing.</p>",
        "ggY2hH_XtMS_text": "<ul>\n<li>The above time frame is only applied for orders to the US with standard shipping methods.</li>\n<li>International orders: It may take 2-5 days longer due to the customs clearance process.</li>\n<li><strong>Orders can be cancelled or modified only within 2 hours after being placed.</strong></li>\n<li>Learn more about Shipping Policy <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/shipping-policy\">here.</a>\n</li>\n<li>For more detailed information and instructions, please visit our<a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/refund-policy\"><span style=\"color:rgb(22,95,83);\"> </span>Refund &amp; Replacement Policy.</a>\n</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggVI69kLduJ_text": "<ul>\n<li>Full-refund or replace a new item (No any extra fee within 30 days since your purchase) for faulty, defective or damaged products.</li>\n<li>Full-refund if the item is not as described.</li>\n<li>We have 24/7/365 ticket and email support. Please contact us at <i>support@hapyco.co</i> if you need any assistance.</li>\n<li>For more detailed information and instructions, please visit our <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/refund-policy\">Refund &amp; Replacement Policy.</a>\n</li>\n</ul>",
        "gg9djR-c3ZU_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "ggHxm-K0LAX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggWSJUxnYcX_text": "<p>The most comfortable… </p>",
        "gg5g09zhY8N_text": "<p>Absolutely the most comfortable underwear I’ve ever bought. They fit perfectly, stay in place, and feel like a second skin.</p>",
        "gg-tUtWxKhh_text": "<p>Liam H.</p>",
        "ggs_s6lEDOC_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggSV8qjUIF1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggaAE89r1UW_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands but..</p>",
        "ggcrnmF_lIE_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands, but these boxers are on a whole different level. They’re incredibly soft, supportive, and durable.</p>",
        "ggLi9e3uAk2_text": "<p>Olivier J.</p>",
        "ggAGzVndjra_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggeny5F_KBU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gg1o0gkxDYu_text": "<p>As an avid runner </p>",
        "ggiBPVdR7g-_text": "<p>As a runner, finding the right underwear is crucial. These offer excellent support and breathability. They keep me dry and comfortable</p>",
        "ggJai-mIzBo_text": "<p>Avery N.</p>",
        "gg5qyYTYLNz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggRSQR38XsP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gghO-CfoMnU_text": "<p>No odor or sweat, this bamboo really works!</p>",
        "ggdBeG9LSOZ_text": "<p>My partner says they’re the most comfortable he’s ever worn. After multiple washes, they keep their shape and softness.</p>",
        "ggFJhv6XtFa_text": "<p>Camelia J.</p>",
        "ggNfcoKkxKB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg6_EEbztta_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggMh8UP1KeW_text": "<p>Satisfied beyond belief!!!! </p>",
        "ggpTskvks_G_text": "<p>Two weeks of walking around Europe, constantly adjusting and sweating. After switching to Boxhero, the comfort blew me away. 100% satisfied!</p>",
        "ggAEVbUSJBl_text": "<p>Marc C.</p>",
        "gg-oS0OaV7f_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg_q4SQCEgL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggMXtYiLE4i_text": "<p>UNREAL comfort</p>",
        "ggZ5ZjGQGbG_text": "<p>These boxers are like a hug—soft, supportive, and luxurious. They stay in place all day, even after multiple washes. </p>",
        "ggiCWw-UEx6_text": "<p>Jason K.</p>",
        "ggD_fPnY0sn_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg8vkzyRom3_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-f2ab390a-662e-4a0e-bf4c-237bc7b9d578.svg",
        "ggLbdEuXnjp_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.6</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>3800+ Customers.</u></strong></span></p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_625369883093238323": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369883093238323",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "e8a29fa9d400e9083bde08075623e07959f67498d17092c7774088442fb66233_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggbH-IVQ7BE_text": "<p>4.8/5 based on 3438 reviews</p>",
        "gga1VaOr4fd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_12_19_30.png?v=1782296453",
        "ggmAceQtFS9_text": "50,481+",
        "gglsj97MMsI_text": "Happy Customers",
        "ggPmGwwLfeb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_12_33_27.png",
        "ggCE7fHYrbV_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Ridiculous but Amazing</span>",
        "ggyX7DdMLJ__text": "<p>The shirt is adorable. I used a picture of our cat and it came out really clear. I was worried because the photo I uploaded wasn’t the best quality, but Hapyco still made it look great. My husband said it’s “ridiculous but amazing” and that’s exactly what I wanted.</p>",
        "ggT835CQDCm_text": "<p>Carole j.</p>",
        "ggL1j6OyWH8_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggHo-yWyVXU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/fb43eaae-d2f0-4193-9018-ebd2b719b100.png",
        "gg7uT70rLT8_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">The Perfect Gift for My Husband</span>",
        "ggpcGRoEQhT_text": "<p>The shirt came out way better than I expected. I ordered it with pictures of our two dogs for my husband and he literally just stood there smiling when he opened it. The colors were bright, the dogs looked so clear, and the whole thing felt really personal. He wore it the same night to dinner and everyone kept asking where I got it from. The only thing I would say is it took a little longer than I thought to arrive, but honestly it was worth the wait.</p>",
        "gguY7QvohhM_text": "<p>ron d.</p>",
        "gg2EiQA_kVZ_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggKp4y8aDpK_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_12_25_25.png",
        "ggbNlt912uz_text": "My Dad Showed Everyone",
        "ggaIIux6kpV_text": "<p>I got this for my dad for Father’s Day and he absolutely loved it. He doesn’t usually get emotional over gifts but when he saw our old dog on the shirt he got quiet for a second and said “this is actually really cool.” That alone made it worth it. Thank you Hapyco.</p>",
        "gghbdWf1S0I_text": "<p>Tommy G.</p>",
        "ggXodWLXYj9_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggvOiRjsRSc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_13_02_19.png",
        "ggtXh0XHscb_text": "Everyone Loved It at the BBQ",
        "ggWYmWxn-eN_text": "<p>This shirt was a huge hit for my boyfriend’s birthday. I put our cat on it as a joke at first but when it arrived it looked so good that it didn’t even feel like a joke anymore. He wore it to his birthday BBQ and people were stopping him all day to look at it. The quality was nicer than I expected too. Super fun gift.</p>",
        "ggB0JxMJuZo_text": "<p>Samuel p.</p>",
        "ggjmKYCRCBG_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_12_29_23.png",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Capture_d_ecran_2025-03-31_a_09.39.51.png",
        "gga14oHm6kL_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">Almost Perfect and So Meaningful</span>",
        "ggoFT06VXY4_text": "<p>I ordered one for my husband with our dog Max on it and it came out almost perfect. The print is beautiful and the picture looks exactly like him. My husband laughed first, then he actually got emotional because Max passed last year. The shirt fit him well, but the sleeves were maybe a tiny bit bigger than expected. Still, he said it’s one of the best gifts I’ve ever given him.</p>",
        "ggsa-JkQbqv_text": "<p>Alex N.</p>",
        "ggiUNvvbYkT_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggaplnOalc2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_13_00_52.png",
        "ggj55v5oBWj_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">So Cute and Bright</span>",
        "ggWpEm7o-W0_text": "<p>Honestly I wasn’t sure how the photo would look on a Hawaiian shirt, but it came out so cute. The colors are bright, the fabric is light, and my dog’s face is everywhere in the funniest way. My husband has already worn it twice.</p>",
        "ggSo3tb0KO9_text": "<p>John M.</p>",
        "ggqtOcmPD1Q_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "gg1AzXVMlQj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/82c86c12-711e-4d7b-b65b-2eee4c213244.png",
        "ggtb5aRMmlI_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Strangers Kept Complimenting Him</span>",
        "ggcmHQakp1d_text": "<p>Bought this for my fiancé and he loved it. We went out for drinks and strangers kept complimenting the shirt. He was proud telling everyone it was our dog on it. Such a cool idea and really good quality.</p>",
        "ggBEBA7Z0To_text": "<p>Walt f.</p>",
        "ggSRlEt7zg6_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggTzJSpgZ7w_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/8d6d03bc-bbac-4820-9c73-077514b8d444.png",
        "ggW6i3PixrQ_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Best Gift of the Party</span>",
        "ggErwWMd-6O_text": "<p>I surprised my brother with this shirt for his 40th birthday with his bulldog printed all over it. He opened it in front of everyone and the whole room started laughing and cheering. Then he put it on right away and didn’t take it off the whole night. The shirt was definitely the best gift of the party.</p>",
        "ggxQbXj5HuA_text": "<p>Jeff C.</p>",
        "ggNL_LQAxfd_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_625369882925466163": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369882925466163",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "9a5460415ec433dbbc15cf9ebd4d20b4ce04fd53edd4d5753a43a5dea93f4d5f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "FAQ",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p>Still have questions ? Check here</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p>What is bamboo fibre and why is it used for boxer shorts?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p>Why do dermatologists recommend bamboo fibre boxers? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p>How does the breathability of bamboo fibre boxers differ from other materials? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p>What does the “buy 2 + 3 free” offer mean? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_4": "<p>How does the durability of bamboo fibre boxers compare to traditional boxers? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_5": "<p>Are bamboo fibre boxers suitable for sensitive skin? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_6": "<p>Can I wash bamboo fibre boxers in the washing machine? </p>",
        "ggRO0x1JBf5_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre is a natural material that’s increasingly appreciated for its soft, breathable, and environmentally friendly properties. It’s used in the manufacture of our boxer shorts to provide optimal comfort and promote better intimate hygiene.</p>",
        "ggXHYiMjwOM_text": "<p>Dermatologists recommend our bamboo fibre boxers because of their softness and their ability to reduce unpleasant friction, helping to maintain impeccable hygiene in intimate areas.</p>",
        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>The exceptional breathability of our bamboo fibre boxers allows air to circulate, reducing humidity and perspiration. You will always feel comfortable and fresh, whatever your activity.</p>",
        "ggrxGymrlkU_text": "<p>Our special offer allows you to buy 2 bamboo fibre boxer shorts and receive 3 free. This is a limited opportunity to renew your collection of high-quality underwear. Not to be missed!</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre boxer shorts are designed for added durability thanks to their high-quality material. They are more resistant to wear and last longer than regular boxers.</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>Yes, in general, bamboo fibre boxers are suitable for sensitive skin due to their softness and ability to reduce skin irritation. However, if you have specific concerns, we recommend consulting a healthcare professional.</p>",
        "ggkYAJ7acNt_text": "<p>Yes, our bamboo fibre boxers are machine-washable. Please follow the care instructions included with your boxers for best washing practices.</p>",
        "ggQ0Wtpv_Ah_label": "<p>TRY IT RISK-FREE – TODAY AT 50% OFF!</p>",
        "ggmkvDRWsjL_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-day</strong></span> money -back guarantee</p>",
        "ggxet32tdWW_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns</strong></span><strong>,</strong> NO QUESTIONS ASKED </p>"
      }
    },
